  "title": "BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT INTERNSHIP (B2B)",
  "description": "<p>Step beyond the classroom and into a dynamic business environment where your ideas, energy, and ambition truly matter. This internship is crafted to give you hands-on experience, real responsibilities, and guided mentorship that helps you grow with confidence. No prior experience needed, training will be provided!<br /></p><p>WHAT YOU WILL EXPERIENCE<br /></p><p>As a Business Development Intern, you’ll take part in exciting, real-world projects that help shape client relationships and business strategies.<br /></p><p>•⁠  Collaborate closely with senior executives on daily business operations</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Profile and identify potential business clients</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Understand client needs and help craft tailored recommendations</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Build and maintain strong client relationships</p><p>•⁠  Assist in campaign and branding initiatives</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Sit in on meetings to observe real-time decision making</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Share fresh ideas and contribute to strategic discussions</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Work with cross-functional teams on ongoing projects and campaigns<br /></p><p>WHO WE’RE LOOKING FOR<br /></p><p>A great candidate isn’t defined by experience but by attitude, curiosity, and willingness to learn.<br /></p><p>•⁠  ⁠A strong communicator who enjoys connecting with others</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Friendly, confident, and team-oriented</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Ready to learn, proactive, and not afraid to take initiative</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Interested in business, marketing, sales, or client service</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Reliable, responsible, and committed to personal development<br /></p><p>WHAT YOU’LL GAIN<br /></p><p>Grow. Learn. Elevate Yourself.<br /></p><p>•⁠  ⁠Mentorship from experienced senior executives</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Real-world business development and client management experience</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Improved communication, leadership, and teamwork skills</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Exposure to strategic planning and professional meetings</p><p>•⁠  ⁠A supportive environment to grow your strengths and explore new paths</p><p>•⁠  A stepping stone toward future roles in business, marketing, sales, consulting, or entrepreneurship</p>",
